        Guitar class's
    </strong>
    The Beginners Guitar Class takes place Thursday 3.30-4.30 pm this is for youth's who are only beginning to learn how to play the guitar, 4.30-5.30pm is for those who are more intermediate and a little older in age &  Our Advanced Guitar class is more for young teen's who have experience and that class takes Place 5.30pm-6.30pm. Classes will cost €15 this term as there are 3 classes this term €5 each. Normally there are 5 classes a term and in total costing €25. Please feel free to contact the center if you have any questions or need further information. Pre-registration is required.
</p>
